			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1772821271643,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nSolid boxes = Docker containers\nTest traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\nTLS (testbed CA), IPsec overlay,\nHTTPS/HTTP3, WebRTC conferencing\n\nProductivity: http(s)://172.16.0.10\nStreaming: http(s)://172.16.0.11\nConferencing: wss://172.16.0.12:8443",
			"rawText": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nSolid boxes = Docker containers\nTest traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\nTLS (testbed CA), IPsec overlay,\nHTTPS/HTTP3, WebRTC conferencing\n\nProductivity: http(s)://172.16.0.10\nStreaming: http(s)://172.16.0.11\nConferencing: wss://172.16.0.12:8443",
			"fontSize": 16,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nSolid boxes = Docker containers\nTest traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\nTLS (testbed CA), IPsec overlay,\nHTTPS/HTTP3, WebRTC conferencing\n\nProductivity: http(s)://172.16.0.10\nStreaming: http(s)://172.16.0.11\nConferencing: wss://172.16.0.12:8443",
